headline: Accenture CEO Julie Sweet says there’s one thing you should never do if you get offered a big job you don’t feel ready for
summary: Having the confidence to say “yes” to a stretch role can open doors you never expected to be unlocked, just like Accenture CEO Julie Sweet.
